  "status": "Final",
  "summary": "This EIP proposes a new extension for NFTs (non-fungible token, aka [EIP-721](./eip-721.md)): nft-hyperlink-extention (hNFT), embedding NFTs with hyperlinks, referred to as \u201chNFTs\u201d. As owners of hNFTs, users may authorize a URL slot to a specific address which can be either an externally-owned account (EOA) or a contract address and hNFT owners are entitled to revoke that authorization at any time. The address which has slot authorization can manage the URL of that slot.",
  "title": "NFT Hyperlink Extension"
